CustomField.description: Stores the size/volume of output (resulting) data for the task/query that's being measured (if applicable). For example if you are measuring a named query execution you could place here the number of records that is contained in the result set.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Stores the size/volume of output (resulting) data for the task/query that's being measured (if applicable). For example if you are measuring a named query execution you could place here the number of records that is contained in the result set.
CustomField.label: Output Data Volume
